VISA POLICY OF OMAN
Visitors to Oman must obtain a visa prior to travel unless they come from one of the visa exempt countries , or if they 're citizens of a country allowing them to get a visa on arrival .
Citizens of member nations of the Gulf Cooperation Council may travel to Oman without visa limits .
Nationals of 71 other countries and territories can apply for visas online which are valid for a period of 30 days .
All visitors must hold a passport valid for 6 months .
