CONDITIONAL EVISA Section::::Conditional eVisa .
Citizens of the following 25 countries , including their spouses and children of another nationality , can obtain an online eVisa , if they hold a valid Schengen Visa , a valid visa from Australia , Canada , Japan , the United Kingdom , or the United States , or a residence permit from one of these countries .
One can apply for a single - entry visa ( 5 OMR for 10 days or 20 OMR 30 days ) , or 1-year - valid multiple - entry visa ( for 50 OMR ) .
The allowed duration of stay is 10 days for 10 days visa and 30 days for other visas ( or 30 days per visit on the multiple - entry visa ) .
